overview:
Voicebuy was created mainly to make wholesale VoIP termination process automatic and fast for small and medium-sized VoIP providers.

The company is dealing with around 100 vendors in Europe, North America, Middle East and Africa, providing them with high quality VoIP Termination Services, affordable at competitive rates and most favorable prices.

Through the delivery of the best wholesale SIP services, we meet the needs of the most demanding VoIP resellers, broadening our cover zone with every passing day!

Voicebuy offers you Business and Mobile VoIP Solutions as well. You can upgrade you web access to Voicebuy free hosted PBX.

To make it complete Voicebuy provides you with the opportunities to purchase DID or virtual Numbers and forward them to your SIP account building your complete business phone network.
